wdi-EN.ATM.CO2E.EG.ZS.name: CO2 intensity
wdi-EN.ATM.CO2E.EG.ZS.source: Carbon Dioxide Information Analysis Center, Environmental Sciences Division, Oak Ridge National Laboratory, Tennessee, United States.
wdi-EN.ATM.CO2E.EG.ZS.units: kg per kg of oil equivalent energy use
